window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Frank returned to his world to find everything's wrong. Did the events of the past change the present, or is there something larger at work here?</p> <p>He sets off to retrieve the stolen stones from the time compass. Along the way, he'll learn new skills, new crafting, and find a new side to himself he never could've anticipated.</p> <p>New, unexpected team members also can't be ruled out in this harem time-travel fun.</p>"; 
